<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُنْقَلَبًا}</span> ... مَرْجِعًا وَمَرَدًّا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّكِنَّا}</span> ... لَكنْ أَنَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حُسْبَانًا}</span> ... عَذَابًا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَعِيدًا زَلَقًا}</span> ... أَرْضًا مَلْسَاءَ جَرْدَاءَ لَا تَثْبُتُ عَلَيْهَا قَدَمٌ، وَلَا تُنْبِتُ شَيْئًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَوْرًا}</span> ... غَائِرًا ذَاهِبًا فِي عُمْقِ الأَرْضِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُحِيطَ بِثَمَرِهِ}</span> ... أُهْلِكَتْ أَمْوَالُهُ، وَحَدِيقَتُهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُقَلِّبُ كَفَّيْهِ}</span> ... كِنَايَةٌ عَنِ النَّدَامَةِ وَالحَسْرَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَاوِيَةٌ عَلَى عُرُوشِهَا}</span> ... سَاقِطَةٌ بَعْضُهَا عَلَى بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
